CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 2, 1961, pg. 13A, reads: "LEAVING CHURCH - Mr. and Mrs. Richard M. Prunty are shown leaving the Sixth Mt. Zion Church, following their recent wedding. The bride is the former Romaine W. Henderson, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Mack Henderson Sr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Richard M. Prunty, and bride Romaine W. Henderson Prunty wearing lace gown with tiered skirt, standing in doorway of Sixth Mt. Zion Baptist Church
